Because you are on Business, you should have access to Portals through your Settings > Branding.

Portals is less an explicit product, and more the ability to Whitelist your cloud instance of Retool and utilize <a href="https://docs.retool.com/org-users/guides/user-permissions" target="_blank">User Permissions</a> and <a href="https://docs.retool.com/org-users/guides/workspaces" target="_blank">Workspaces</a> to give specific users access to specific apps without any Retool Branding.